text: Wicked is a 2024 American musical fantasy movie directed by Jon M. Chu and written by Winnie Holzman and Dana Fox. It is the first movie of a two-part movie series of the stage musical of the same name by Stephen Schwartz and Holzman. ==Cast== The movie stars Cynthia Erivo, Ariana Grande-Butera, Jonathan Bailey, Ethan Slater, Bowen Yang, Marissa Bode, Peter Dinklage, Michelle Yeoh and Jeff Goldblum. ==References== == Other websites == * * Category:2024 musical movies Category:2020s fantasy movies Category:Movies based on musicals Category:Universal Pictures movies Category:American musical fantasy movies Category:Movies about animals Category:Movies about friendship Category:Movies about sisters Category:Movies based on fairy tales
